,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:04:33.000Z","msg":"大字報成日都話有汽油彈、燃燒彈<br />\n但係我到依家都未見過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b132a35fdf0359badaed9fe01df2ddfb4f442e01","tid":1434329,"uid":225002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:25:54.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"eb054860e9f65ef9bea8f4ce5108ec8d5ab8a7aa","tid":1434329,"uid":225002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:31:30.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d4c5ac22f0e94c5da8b98abd1296b17d85630737","tid":1434329,"uid":225002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:33:53.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fdaaca778a575e9894620a03b1ec5b3e169f1ed1","tid":1434329,"uid":225002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:46:15.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"93c7c5990a370e45eb9e1c147472147f2733560e","tid":1434329,"uid":265695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:47:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de03959a2a1fc1703d080def750151254ecadfaf","tid":1434329,"uid":5205,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:48:48.000Z","msg":"Starcraft"},{"pid":"02a5f3f09ead8d73c1d215d487365bf480d38eef","tid":1434329,"uid":225002,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:54:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/o4Z0BTmzRgg/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2Fo4Z0BTmzRgg%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=154bdfdb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>aoc 我好鐘意用佢來防守。高攻 + area attack，用來掃步兵一流。D速攻步兵係一炮死，對家知道我有哩部野之後，通常唔會貿貿然進攻。</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"6b065885c170f43ac2fd5230bf796ed6c6f1f4b0","tid":1434329,"uid":225002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:59:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>歷史上來講，我覺得哩部野唔係太難整，最緊要係有一條有彈性嘅弓弦。如果無弓箭嘅話，我覺得就地攞石頭都OK。</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"8b28a89302113bbfdbed40bc5c53f58bfd9ebfd6","tid":1434329,"uid":225002,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:03:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>致各位帶風狗，我會好好照顧哩個post。Under my watch，no 風 can be 帶。 </strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"4c3c7cc3dfc6b09c1ff34d7078e8c005973211ca","tid":1434329,"uid":225002,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:25:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>講返正題，scorpion 弓炮於我而言，係用來防守多過進攻嘅。係每條防線，我都會放一至兩部，但當然要放係城墻後邊啦，跟住係左右隔離放滿盾兵之類。有時對家會放大絕去破你，咁你就連兵帶炮向後退，等佢放完再隊返前。<br />\n<br />\n有D玩家更聰明嘅，會放大絕嘅同時all-in所有步兵突擊。咁你就要有先見之明，預先每粒兵都upgrade粉紅護罩保護，之後兵同炮都唔退，同佢打一場硬仗。<br />\n<br />\n但當然啦，我係講緊你嘅兵員多佢兩倍而上，而且確保每一個都打得嘅情況底下，先之打。唔係嘅話，就撤退為上。</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"89ecf4fd693715335a45d3b1277e97c70e75416d","tid":1434329,"uid":137309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:39:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6b62a8178cfc8d49da1b84a6c9058bfb3cc768f0","tid":1434329,"uid":225002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:45:10.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"563dea6b47db790a262a92c75aaf2033a04b7f00","tid":1434329,"uid":32699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:58:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eb00fefaf21b50a2594d21e2028354ed257e46ce","tid":1434329,"uid":32699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:59:06.000Z","msg":"作為打機友我真係好認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6da05e395e53478694b2e3ca1a715fe22106bfbc","tid":1434329,"uid":225002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci